Author: fishonthesun
Text: This is really awesome!!! I also had a big an nutritious breakfast and it feels amazing. Like I didnt undereat where I wasnt hungry but wasnt full and I didnt eat to the point I felt like I'd burst. I just ate until I felt the first signs of fullness and called it quits. I havent done that in literal years

Text: This is amazing!!! Good for you, you should be proud!
